OL,5, The mistreatment of patients at a      
OL,6, mental health hospital does warrant a  
OL,7, public inquiry, a health minister has  
OL,8, said.                                  
OL,10,FWill Quince apologised to patients at  
OL,11,Fthe Edenfield Centre in Prestwich near 
OL,12,FManchester and their families.         
OL,14,FA BBC Panorama investigation found a   
OL,15,F"toxic culture of humiliation, verbal  
OL,16,Fabuse and bullying" at the hospital.   
OL,18,FHospital bosses said they took         
OL,19,Fimmediate action including suspending  
OL,20,Fstaff and launching a clinical review. 
